name: edgeworker_edgeserverflow
sql:
(edgeworker_edgeserverflow) -> multiIf (
  edgeworker_edgeserverflow = 'a',
  'subWorkers disabled',
  edgeworker_edgeserverflow = 'n',
  'Normal flow',
  edgeworker_edgeserverflow = 's',
  'Akamai JavaScript execution engine not available',
  edgeworker_edgeserverflow = 'r',
  'Termination request',
  edgeworker_edgeserverflow = 'T',
  'Akamai edge server write timeout',
  edgeworker_edgeserverflow = 't',
  'Akamai edge server read timeout',
    edgeworker_edgeserverflow = 'e',
  'EdgeWorkers returned error',
    edgeworker_edgeserverflow = 'E',
  'Bad input from EdgeWorkers',
    edgeworker_edgeserverflow = 'u',
  'Unexpected Termination Request for non-METHOD_GET method',
   edgeworker_edgeserverflow = 'm',
  'Error in applying EdgeWorkers commands',
   edgeworker_edgeserverflow = 'c',
  'EdgeWorkers result applied from cached results',
     edgeworker_edgeserverflow = 'o',
  'Other',
  edgeworker_edgeserverflow
)
